            <h2>Hi, I'm Chas.</h2>
            <p>I'm one of the co-founders of <a href="https://www.aptible.com" target="_blank">Aptible</a>. I'm a developer and enterpreneur with a background in regulatory law. I live and work in Manhattan.</p>
